---
import SiteLayout from "~/components/layouts/site-layout/index.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
    head={{
        title: "Shihab Mahamud - Full-stack developer",
        description: "Software developer from bangladesh. I mainly work with Laravel, React & WordPress."
    }}
>
    <div class="max-w-md">
        <h1 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-extrabold text-black">Who the hell am I?</h1>
        <div class="text-grey-darkest spaced-y-6 text-lg leading-normal">
            <p>
                I'm <a href="https://twitter.com/adamwathan" class="font-bold text-black">@adamwathan</a>, a full-stack
                developer, entrepreneur, and <a
                    href="https://twitter.com/mijustin/status/1065299912013709312"
                    class="font-bold text-black">Justin's worst nightmare</a
                >.
            </p>
            <p>
                I share everything I know about making awesome software through my <a
                    href="/articles"
                    class="font-bold text-black">articles</a
                >, <a href="/talks" class="font-bold text-black">talks</a>, <a
                    href="/screencasts"
                    class="font-bold text-black">screencasts</a
                >, <a href="/podcast" class="font-bold text-black">podcast</a>, and <a
                    href="/courses"
                    class="font-bold text-black">courses</a
                >.
            </p>
            <p>
                In 2016, I released my first book and left my job to <a href="/projects" class="font-bold text-black"
                    >make things</a
                > full-time that help other developers build better software.
            </p>
            <p>
                Right now I'm working on <a href="/going-full-time-on-tailwind-css" class="font-bold text-black"
                    >Tailwind CSS</a
                >, and I share updates about my progress in my <a href="/journal" class="font-bold text-black"
                    >work journal</a
                >.
            </p>
            <p>
                Curious about how I work? Check out my <a href="/uses" class="font-bold text-black">uses</a>
                page for a full list of all the software, gadgets, and services I use.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</SiteLayout>
